![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8c8be69d-ce0f-4d79-ac80-6d6436767146/e354.jpg)

In this action-packed episode of the Major Issues Podcast, the hosts dive headfirst into _Hit-Monkey_ Season 2, unpacking all the wild twists, sharp humor, and intense action that make this series a must-watch. From the jaw-dropping moments to the deeper character arcs, the gang dissects the highs, the lows, and everything in between. Whether you're a seasoned fan or a first-time viewer, you won't want to miss this full-throttle breakdown of what Season 2 delivers and why it's even more chaotic (and brilliant!) than ever before. Get ready for a killer conversation as we talk _Hit-Monkey_’s blood-soaked journey into the heart of vengeance!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

